It is assumed you have OpenGrm Thrax version 1.2.1 or higher installed. If you
do not then the first thing to do is go to:

http://openfst.cs.nyu.edu/twiki/bin/view/GRM/Thrax

and follow the instructions there.

Paul Dixon's Windows port can be found at:

http://openfst.cs.nyu.edu/twiki/bin/view/Contrib/OpenGrmThraxWin

Once Thrax is installed you should do the following in this directory:

thraxmakedep verbalize.grm
make
